## Tag Migration Strategy

### Phase 1: Audit Current Tags

1. List all existing tags
2. Identify duplicates and near-duplicates
3. Map to standard taxonomy
4. Create consolidation plan

### Phase 2: Standardize Existing Rules

1. Update rule frontmatter with standard tags
2. Add missing mandatory tags
3. Remove redundant tags
4. Limit to 5-7 tags maximum

### Phase 3: Enforce for New Rules

1. Require standard tags in new rules
2. Validate against taxonomy
3. Review in code review process

