## Tag Discovery and Search

### Finding Rules by Tag

**Grep command:**
```powershell
# Find all rules with specific tag
Get-ChildItem ".cursor/rules" -Recurse -Filter "*.mdc" | Select-String -Pattern "tags:.*\bdevelopment\b"

# Find rules with multiple tags
Get-ChildItem ".cursor/rules" -Recurse -Filter "*.mdc" | Select-String -Pattern "tags:.*\bdevelopment\b.*\btesting\b"
```

**Common search patterns:**
- All persona files: `grep -r "tags:.*persona"`
- All critical rules: `grep -r "tags:.*critical"`
- All git-related: `grep -r "tags:.*git"`
- All documentation rules: `grep -r "tags:.*documentation"`

