## Prohibited Tags

### ❌ Never Use These Tags

| Avoid | Reason | Use Instead |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| `general` | Too vague | Specific domain tag |
| `misc` | Meaningless | Specific category |
| `other` | Non-descriptive | Specific purpose |
| `temp` | Temporary indicator | Remove or use proper tag |
| `old` | Version indicator | Use `version` field |
| `new` | Not informative | Use `version` field |
| `important` | Use `priority` field | `critical` tag or priority field |
| `urgent` | Subjective | Use priority field |

