## Verification Checklist

Before committing rules with tags:

- [ ] At least 1 Rule Type tag present
- [ ] At least 1 Domain tag present
- [ ] Tags follow kebab-case format
- [ ] Tags are singular form
- [ ] Maximum 7 tags
- [ ] No prohibited tags used
- [ ] Tags match standard taxonomy
- [ ] No duplicate/redundant tags

